    <section name="Introduction">
        <subsection name="What is the Hippo Forge Maven Skin?">
            <p>
              The Hippo Forge Maven Skin is a Maven site skin based on
              <a href="http://maven.apache.org/skins/maven-fluido-skin">Apache Maven Fluido Skin</a>.
              That skin is based on <a href="http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap">Twitter's bootstrap</a> frontend framework.
            </p>
        </subsection>
        <subsection name="Documentation">
          <p>To see how to use the skin in your project's Maven site, see <a href="usage.html">the usage page</a>.</p>
          <p>To see how the skin looks on various HTML elements, see <a href="typography.html">the typography page</a>.</p>
          <p>For the latest version and changes, see the <a href="release-notes.html">release notes</a>.</p>
        </subsection>
      </section>
